<p>
THANK YOU!

<p>
I feel like I need a recovery program from the last 3 1/2 years in AA. For the last
year I have really struggled with the feeling that something is not quite right.
The only advice anyone, including my sponsor, had to give was to go to more
meetings, do more service work, blah, blah, blah.  No one would listen.  I was
