site helped with that decision as well. It's hard to understand
how the folks that are so devoted to quitting alcohol and other drugs can
rationalize their continued use of tobacco! It's insane! I find it amusing that
they say in NA &quot;we abstain from all mood and mind altering substances&quot;. No they
don't! Stop smoking tobacco and see just how &quot;mind and mood altering&quot; that
substance is when you try to quit!

<p>
